## 📊 **状态管理设计**

### Android 状态 (Bundle)

```java
// 保存状态
@Override
protected void onSaveInstanceState(Bundle outState) {
    super.onSaveInstanceState(outState);
    outState.putString("time", textClock.getText().toString());
    outState.putString("location", locationView.getText().toString());
}

// 恢复状态
@Override
protected void onCreate(Bundle savedInstanceState) {
    super.onCreate(savedInstanceState);
    if (savedInstanceState != null) {
        String time = savedInstanceState.getString("time");
        String location = savedInstanceState.getString("location");
        // 恢复 UI
    }
}
```

### HarmonyOS 状态 (@State)

```typescript
@Component
struct MainPage {
    @State textClockValue: string = '';      // 自动持久化
    @State locationText: string = '';        // 自动持久化
    @State isRunning: boolean = false;       // 自动持久化

    // @State 装饰器会自动处理状态管理
    // 数据变化时自动重新渲染
}
